{"tid":2395456,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登停止川普撤軍德國政策 並重新審視兵力部署","createTime":"2021-02-05T02:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:41:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb2db0ae95c20e17c201eb951baa3f40f89a585","tid":2395456,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登已正式停止川普政府去年下令從德國撤軍的計畫。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，川普撤軍德國計畫並未執行。拜登周四（4日）在國務院發表講話表示，在國防部長奧斯汀（Lloyd Austin）審視美國駐軍情況之前，將停止撤軍。拜登表示，奧斯汀將確保軍事部署和我們的外交政策、國安優先保持一致。<br />\n<br />\n川普指控德國長期拖欠北大西洋公約組織（NATO），去年宣布削減駐德國的美軍，由現時3.45萬人減至2.5萬人，裁減約9500人。他又警告，美方決定撤走部分士兵，直至德國投入足夠的國防開支。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n川普這項撤軍命令遭國會以及軍方抵制，因為軍方長期以來一直依賴德國這個重要盟友和行動基地。川普一再指控北約的歐盟國家占美國便宜，並未依照承諾支付至少2%國內生產毛額（GDP）的防衛支出，且過度依賴美國。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210205/HHYFDQDISZFMLFYI3WWVWGDWPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210205%2FHHYFDQDISZFMLFYI3WWVWGDWPM%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ER21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=92754470\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210205%2FHHYFDQDISZFMLFYI3WWVWGDWPM%2F&h=a483e3ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210205/HHYFDQDISZFMLFYI3WWVWGDWPM/</a><br />\n<br />\n（呂青倚／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"78deded5f292addbdd13fc008db85e9a43fd4095","tid":2395456,"uid":85629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:08:29.000Z","msg":"依賴德國有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b57e3bd61e6ddab6fc6c4deefff3bb7d2bde81c","tid":2395456,"uid":8308,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"德國咪有老解幫手囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b955cad1c6b8c4c5237ed5e2b972d84eb01144fc","tid":2395456,"uid":52946,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:11: